      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so if the ph is too high, the iron is still in the dirt but the plant just cant grab it? i dont get how that works chemically though. like how does a change in ph actually stop the roots from taking it up? is it a chemical reaction or something?",
      "source": "evaluator"
